title: THURSDAY 4/29 - JAGUARS ARE ON THE CLOCK!
itunes:title: THURSDAY 4/29 - JAGUARS ARE ON THE CLOCK!
description:
The NFL draft is finally here! Jaguars head coach Urban Meyer (0:12) talks about preparing for the first pick in the draft. The 49ers picking third, expected to take a QB, but tight end George Kittle (1:16) still believes in Jimmy Garoppolo. The Falcons sitting at pick #4, could go couple different directions. GM Terry Fontenot (2:10) says he'll have to wait to see how things play out ahead of their pick. The Broncos trading for Teddy Bridgewater (3:02), while the Buccaneers bring back Antonio Brown (3:17). Cowboys QB Dak Prescott (3:30) healing up nicely, and Pete Carroll (3:42) says things are all good between the Seahawks and Russell Wilson
